---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="C. York — AI strategist, writer, and organizational transformation leader."
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 py-16">
    <p class="text-accent font-mono text-sm mb-3 tracking-wide">About</p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-8">C. York</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none text-gray-300 space-y-6">
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
        I'm an AI strategist and thought leader focused on helping organizations understand and deploy artificial intelligence in ways that create real, lasting value.
      </p>

      <p class="leading-relaxed">
        With a background spanning technology strategy, organizational change, and AI implementation, I work at the intersection of what's technically possible and what actually works inside complex organizations.
      </p>

      <p class="leading-relaxed">
        I believe the biggest challenges in the AI era aren't technical — they're human. Getting the strategy right, building the right culture, and aligning incentives matters more than picking the right model.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4">What I'm focused on</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-400">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="text-accent mt-1">→</span>
          <span>Building AI strategy frameworks for executive teams and boards</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="text-accent mt-1">→</span>
          <span>Writing about the practical realities of AI adoption at scale</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="text-accent mt-1">→</span>
          <span>Advising organizations on responsible AI governance and deployment</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="text-accent mt-1">→</span>
          <span>Speaking on AI transformation, organizational readiness, and the future of work</span>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mt-10 mb-4">Get in touch</h2>
      <p class="leading-relaxed">
        I'm always interested in conversations with leaders thinking seriously about AI strategy and transformation.
        <a href="/contact" class="text-accent hover:underline">Reach out here</a> or connect with me on
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/cyork" class="text-accent hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
